[
  {
    "bookname": "1 Chronicles",
    "chapter": "21",
    "text": "<p class=\"bodytext\">An <st data-num=\"07854\" class=\"\">adversary</st><n id=\"1\" /> <st data-num=\"05975 05921\">opposed</st><n id=\"2\" /> <st data-num=\"03478\" class=\"\">Israel</st>, <st data-num=\"05496\" class=\"\">inciting</st> <st data-num=\"01732\" class=\"\">David</st> to <st data-num=\"04487\" class=\"\">count</st> how many warriors <st data-num=\"03478\" class=\"\">Israel</st> had.<n id=\"3\" />",
    "verse": "1"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "1 Chronicles",
    "chapter": "21",
    "text": "<st data-num=\"01732\" class=\"\">David</st> <st data-num=\"0559 0413\">told</st> <st data-num=\"03097\" class=\"\">Joab</st> <st data-num=\"0413\" class=\"\">and</st> the <st data-num=\"08269\" class=\"\">leaders</st> of the <st data-num=\"05971\" class=\"\">army</st>,<n id=\"1\" /> \u201c<st data-num=\"01980\" class=\"\">Go</st>, <st data-num=\"05608\" class=\"\">count</st> the <st data-num=\"03478\" class=\"\">number of warriors</st><n id=\"2\" /> from <st data-num=\"0884\" class=\"\">Beer Sheba</st> <st data-num=\"05704\" class=\"\">to</st> <st data-num=\"01835\" class=\"\">Dan</st>. Then <st data-num=\"0935\" class=\"\">bring back</st> a report <st data-num=\"0413\" class=\"\">to</st> me so I may <st data-num=\"03045\" class=\"\">know</st> <st data-num=\"04557\" class=\"\">how many</st> we have.\u201d<n id=\"3\" />",
    "verse": "2"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "1 Chronicles",
    "chapter": "21",
    "text": "<st data-num=\"03097\" class=\"\">Joab</st> <st data-num=\"0559\" class=\"\">replied</st>, \u201cMay the <span class=\"smcaps\"><st data-num=\"03068\" class=\"\">Lord</st></span> <st data-num=\"03254 05921\">make</st> his <st data-num=\"05971\" class=\"\">army</st><n id=\"1\" /> a <st data-num=\"01992 03967\">hundred</st> <st data-num=\"06471\" class=\"\">times</st> <st data-num=\"03254 05921\">larger</st>! My <st data-num=\"0113\" class=\"\">master</st>, O <st data-num=\"04428\" class=\"\">king</st>, do <st data-num=\"03808\" class=\"\">not</st> <st data-num=\"03605\" class=\"\">all</st> of them <st data-num=\"05650\" class=\"\">serve</st> my <st data-num=\"0113\" class=\"\">master</st>? <st data-num=\"04100\" class=\"\">Why</st> does my <st data-num=\"0113\" class=\"\">master</st> <st data-num=\"01245\" class=\"\">want to do</st> <st data-num=\"02063\" class=\"\">this</st>? <st data-num=\"04100\" class=\"\">Why</st> <st data-num=\"01961\" class=\"\">bring</st> <st data-num=\"0819\" class=\"\">judgment</st> on <st data-num=\"03478\" class=\"\">Israel</st>?\u201d<n id=\"2\" /> </p>",
    "verse": "3"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "1 Chronicles",
    "chapter": "21",
    "text": "<p class=\"bodytext\">But the <st data-num=\"04428\" class=\"\">king\u2019s</st> <st data-num=\"01697\" class=\"\">edict</st> <st data-num=\"02388\" class=\"\">stood</st>, <st data-num=\"05921\" class=\"\">despite</st> <st data-num=\"03097\" class=\"\">Joab\u2019s</st> <st data-num=\"05921\" class=\"\">objections</st>.<n id=\"1\" /> So <st data-num=\"03097\" class=\"\">Joab</st> <st data-num=\"03318\" class=\"\">left</st> and <st data-num=\"01980\" class=\"\">traveled</st> <st data-num=\"03605\" class=\"\">throughout</st> <st data-num=\"03478\" class=\"\">Israel</st> before <st data-num=\"0935\" class=\"\">returning</st> to <st data-num=\"03389\" class=\"\">Jerusalem</st>.<n id=\"2\" /> ",
    "verse": "4"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "1 Chronicles",
    "chapter": "21",
    "text": "<st data-num=\"03097\" class=\"\">Joab</st> <st data-num=\"05414\" class=\"\">reported</st> <st data-num=\"0413\" class=\"\">to</st> <st data-num=\"01732\" class=\"\">David</st> the <st data-num=\"04557 04662\">number</st> of <st data-num=\"05971\" class=\"\">warriors</st>.<n id=\"1\" /> In <st data-num=\"03605\" class=\"\">all</st> <st data-num=\"03478\" class=\"\">Israel</st> there <st data-num=\"01961\" class=\"\">were</st> <st data-num=\"0505 0505 03967 0505\">1,100,000</st> <st data-num=\"02719\" class=\"\">sword</st>-<st data-num=\"08025\" class=\"\">wielding</st><n id=\"2\" /> <st data-num=\"0376\" class=\"\">soldiers</st>; <st data-num=\"03063\" class=\"\">Judah</st> alone had <st data-num=\"0702 03967 07657 0505\">470,000</st> <st data-num=\"02719\" class=\"\">sword</st>-<st data-num=\"08025\" class=\"\">wielding</st> <st data-num=\"0376\" class=\"\">soldiers</st>.<n id=\"3\" /> ",
    "verse": "5"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "1 Chronicles",
    "chapter": "21",
    "text": "Now Joab<n id=\"1\" /> did <st data-num=\"03808\" class=\"\">not</st> <st data-num=\"06485 08432\">number</st> <st data-num=\"03878\" class=\"\">Levi</st> and <st data-num=\"01144\" class=\"\">Benjamin</st>, <st data-num=\"03588\" class=\"\">for</st> the <st data-num=\"04428\" class=\"\">king\u2019s</st> <st data-num=\"01697\" class=\"\">edict</st> <st data-num=\"08581 0854\">disgusted</st> <st data-num=\"03097\" class=\"\">him</st>. ",
    "verse": "6"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "1 Chronicles",
    "chapter": "21",
    "text": "<st data-num=\"0430\" class=\"\">God</st> was also <st data-num=\"07489 05869\">offended</st> <st data-num=\"05921\" class=\"\">by</st> <st data-num=\"01697 02088\">it</st>,<n id=\"1\" /> so he <st data-num=\"05221\" class=\"\">attacked</st> <st data-num=\"03478\" class=\"\">Israel</st>. </p>",
    "verse": "7"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "1 Chronicles",
    "chapter": "21",
    "text": "<p class=\"bodytext\"><st data-num=\"01732\" class=\"\">David</st> <st data-num=\"0559\" class=\"\">said</st> <st data-num=\"0413\" class=\"\">to</st> <st data-num=\"0430\" class=\"\">God</st>, \u201cI have <st data-num=\"02398\" class=\"\">sinned</st> <st data-num=\"03966\" class=\"\">greatly</st> <st data-num=\"0834\" class=\"\">by</st> <st data-num=\"06213\" class=\"\">doing</st> <st data-num=\"01697 02088\">this</st>! <st data-num=\"06258\" class=\"\">Now</st>, <st data-num=\"04994\" class=\"\">please</st> <st data-num=\"05674\" class=\"\">remove</st> the <st data-num=\"05771\" class=\"\">guilt</st> of your <st data-num=\"05650\" class=\"\">servant</st>, <st data-num=\"03588\" class=\"\">for</st> I have <st data-num=\"05528\" class=\"\">acted</st> <st data-num=\"03966\" class=\"\">very</st> <st data-num=\"05528\" class=\"\">foolishly</st>.\u201d ",
    "verse": "8"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "1 Chronicles",
    "chapter": "21",
    "text": "The <span class=\"smcaps\"><st data-num=\"03068\" class=\"\">Lord</st></span> <st data-num=\"01696 0413 0559\">told</st> <st data-num=\"01410\" class=\"\">Gad</st>, <st data-num=\"01732\" class=\"\">David\u2019s</st> <st data-num=\"02374\" class=\"\">prophet</st>,<n id=\"1\" /> ",
    "verse": "9"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "1 Chronicles",
    "chapter": "21",
    "text": "\u201c<st data-num=\"01980\" class=\"\">Go</st>, <st data-num=\"01696 0413 0559\">tell</st> <st data-num=\"01732\" class=\"\">David</st>, \u2018<st data-num=\"03541\" class=\"\">This is what</st> the <span class=\"smcaps\"><st data-num=\"03068\" class=\"\">Lord</st></span> <st data-num=\"0559\" class=\"\">says</st>: \u201c<st data-num=\"0589\" class=\"\">I</st> am <st data-num=\"05186 05921\">offering</st> you <st data-num=\"07969\" class=\"\">three</st> forms of <st data-num=\"06213\" class=\"\">judgment</st> from which to choose. <st data-num=\"0977\" class=\"\">Pick</st> <st data-num=\"0259\" class=\"\">one</st> of <st data-num=\"02007\" class=\"\">them</st>.\u201d\u2019\u201d<n id=\"1\" />",
    "verse": "10"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "1 Chronicles",
    "chapter": "21",
    "text": "<st data-num=\"01410\" class=\"\">Gad</st> <st data-num=\"0935\" class=\"\">went</st> <st data-num=\"0413\" class=\"\">to</st> <st data-num=\"01732\" class=\"\">David</st> and <st data-num=\"0559\" class=\"\">told</st> him, \u201c<st data-num=\"03541\" class=\"\">This is what</st> the <span class=\"smcaps\"><st data-num=\"03068\" class=\"\">Lord</st></span> <st data-num=\"0559\" class=\"\">says:</st> \u2018<st data-num=\"06901\" class=\"\">Pick</st> one of these:",
    "verse": "11"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "1 Chronicles",
    "chapter": "21",
    "text": "<st data-num=\"0518 07969\">three</st><n id=\"1\" /> <st data-num=\"08141\" class=\"\">years</st> of <st data-num=\"07458\" class=\"\">famine</st>, <st data-num=\"0518\" class=\"\">or</st> <st data-num=\"07969\" class=\"\">three</st> <st data-num=\"02320\" class=\"\">months</st> being <st data-num=\"05595\" class=\"\">chased</st> <st data-num=\"06440\" class=\"\">by</st> your <st data-num=\"06862\" class=\"\">enemies</st> and <st data-num=\"05381\" class=\"\">struck down</st> by <st data-num=\"0341\" class=\"\">their</st> <st data-num=\"02719\" class=\"\">swords</st>,<n id=\"2\" /> <st data-num=\"0518\" class=\"\">or</st> <st data-num=\"07969\" class=\"\">three</st> <st data-num=\"03117\" class=\"\">days</st> being <st data-num=\"02719\" class=\"\">struck down</st> by the <span class=\"smcaps\"><st data-num=\"03068\" class=\"\">Lord</st></span>, during which a <st data-num=\"01698\" class=\"\">plague</st> will invade the <st data-num=\"0776\" class=\"\">land</st> and the <st data-num=\"04397\" class=\"\">angel</st> of the <span class=\"smcaps\"><st data-num=\"03068\" class=\"\">Lord</st></span> will <st data-num=\"07843\" class=\"\">destroy</st> <st data-num=\"03605\" class=\"\">throughout</st> <st data-num=\"03478\" class=\"\">Israel\u2019s</st> <st data-num=\"01366\" class=\"\">territory</st>.\u2019<n id=\"3\" /> <st data-num=\"06258\" class=\"\">Now</st>, <st data-num=\"07200\" class=\"\">decide</st> <st data-num=\"04100 01697\">what</st> I should <st data-num=\"07725\" class=\"\">tell</st> the one who <st data-num=\"07971\" class=\"\">sent</st> me.\u201d",
    "verse": "12"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "1 Chronicles",
    "chapter": "21",
    "text": "<st data-num=\"01732\" class=\"\">David</st> <st data-num=\"0559\" class=\"\">said</st> <st data-num=\"0413\" class=\"\">to</st> <st data-num=\"01410\" class=\"\">Gad</st>, \u201cI am <st data-num=\"03966\" class=\"\">very</st> <st data-num=\"06862\" class=\"\">upset</st>! I <st data-num=\"04994\" class=\"\">prefer</st> to be <st data-num=\"05307\" class=\"\">attacked</st> <st data-num=\"03027\" class=\"\">by</st> the <span class=\"smcaps\"><st data-num=\"03068\" class=\"\">Lord</st></span>, <st data-num=\"03588\" class=\"\">for</st> his <st data-num=\"07356\" class=\"\">mercy</st> is <st data-num=\"03966\" class=\"\">very</st> <st data-num=\"07227\" class=\"\">great</st>; I do <st data-num=\"0408\" class=\"\">not</st> want to be <st data-num=\"05307\" class=\"\">attacked</st> <st data-num=\"03027\" class=\"\">by</st> <st data-num=\"0120\" class=\"\">men</st>!\u201d<n id=\"1\" /> ",
    "verse": "13"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "1 Chronicles",
    "chapter": "21",
    "text": "So the <span class=\"smcaps\"><st data-num=\"03068\" class=\"\">Lord</st></span> <st data-num=\"05414\" class=\"\">sent</st> a <st data-num=\"01698\" class=\"\">plague</st> through <st data-num=\"03478\" class=\"\">Israel</st>, and <st data-num=\"07657 0505\">70,000</st> <st data-num=\"03478\" class=\"\">Israelite</st> <st data-num=\"0376\" class=\"\">men</st> <st data-num=\"05307\" class=\"\">died</st>. </p>",
    "verse": "14"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "1 Chronicles",
    "chapter": "21",
    "text": "<p class=\"bodytext\"><st data-num=\"0430\" class=\"\">God</st> <st data-num=\"07971\" class=\"\">sent</st> an <st data-num=\"04397\" class=\"\">angel</st><n id=\"1\" /> to <st data-num=\"07843\" class=\"\">ravage</st><n id=\"2\" /> <st data-num=\"03389\" class=\"\">Jerusalem</st>. As he was <st data-num=\"07843\" class=\"\">doing so</st>,<n id=\"3\" /> the <span class=\"smcaps\"><st data-num=\"03068\" class=\"\">Lord</st></span> <st data-num=\"07200\" class=\"\">watched</st><n id=\"4\" /> and <st data-num=\"05162\" class=\"\">relented</st> <st data-num=\"05921\" class=\"\">from</st><n id=\"5\" /> his <st data-num=\"07451\" class=\"\">judgment</st>.<n id=\"6\" /> He <st data-num=\"0559\" class=\"\">told</st> the <st data-num=\"04397\" class=\"\">angel</st> who was <st data-num=\"07843\" class=\"\">destroying</st>, \u201cThat\u2019s <st data-num=\"07227\" class=\"\">enough</st>!<n id=\"7\" /> <st data-num=\"07503 03027\">Stop</st> <st data-num=\"06258\" class=\"\">now</st>!\u201d<n id=\"8\" /> <p class=\"bodytext\">Now the <st data-num=\"04397\" class=\"\">angel</st> of the <span class=\"smcaps\"><st data-num=\"03068\" class=\"\">Lord</st></span> was <st data-num=\"05975\" class=\"\">standing</st> <st data-num=\"05973\" class=\"\">near</st> the <st data-num=\"01637\" class=\"\">threshing floor</st> of <st data-num=\"0771\" class=\"\">Ornan</st><n id=\"9\" /> the <st data-num=\"02983\" class=\"\">Jebusite</st>. ",
    "verse": "15"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "1 Chronicles",
    "chapter": "21",
    "text": "<st data-num=\"01732\" class=\"\">David</st> <st data-num=\"05869\" class=\"\">looked</st> <st data-num=\"05375\" class=\"\">up</st> and <st data-num=\"07200\" class=\"\">saw</st> the <st data-num=\"04397\" class=\"\">angel</st> of the <span class=\"smcaps\"><st data-num=\"03068\" class=\"\">Lord</st></span> <st data-num=\"05975\" class=\"\">standing</st> <st data-num=\"0996\" class=\"\">between</st> the <st data-num=\"0776\" class=\"\">earth</st> <st data-num=\"0996\" class=\"\">and</st> <st data-num=\"08064\" class=\"\">sky</st> with his <st data-num=\"02719\" class=\"\">sword</st> <st data-num=\"08025\" class=\"\">drawn</st> and in his <st data-num=\"03027\" class=\"\">hand</st>, <st data-num=\"05186\" class=\"\">stretched out</st> <st data-num=\"05921\" class=\"\">over</st> <st data-num=\"03389\" class=\"\">Jerusalem</st>. <st data-num=\"01732\" class=\"\">David</st> and the <st data-num=\"02205\" class=\"\">leaders</st>, <st data-num=\"03680\" class=\"\">covered</st> with <st data-num=\"08242\" class=\"\">sackcloth</st>, <st data-num=\"05307\" class=\"\">threw</st> themselves <st data-num=\"05307\" class=\"\">down</st> with their <st data-num=\"06440\" class=\"\">faces</st> <st data-num=\"05921\" class=\"\">to the ground</st>.<n id=\"1\" />",
    "verse": "16"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "1 Chronicles",
    "chapter": "21",
    "text": "<st data-num=\"01732\" class=\"\">David</st> <st data-num=\"0559\" class=\"\">said</st> <st data-num=\"0413\" class=\"\">to</st> <st data-num=\"0430\" class=\"\">God</st>, \u201cWas <st data-num=\"0589\" class=\"\">I</st> <st data-num=\"03808\" class=\"\">not</st> the one who <st data-num=\"0559\" class=\"\">decided</st> to <st data-num=\"04487\" class=\"\">number</st> the <st data-num=\"05971\" class=\"\">army</st>? <st data-num=\"0589\" class=\"\">I</st> am the <st data-num=\"01931\" class=\"\">one</st> <st data-num=\"0834\" class=\"\">who</st> <st data-num=\"02398\" class=\"\">sinned</st> and <st data-num=\"07489\" class=\"\">committed</st> this <st data-num=\"07489\" class=\"\">awful deed</st>!<n id=\"1\" /> As for <st data-num=\"0428\" class=\"\">these</st> <st data-num=\"06629\" class=\"\">sheep</st>\u2014<st data-num=\"04100\" class=\"\">what</st> have they <st data-num=\"06213\" class=\"\">done</st>? O <span class=\"smcaps\"><st data-num=\"03068\" class=\"\">Lord</st></span> my <st data-num=\"0430\" class=\"\">God</st>, <st data-num=\"01961 04994 03027\">attack</st> me and my <st data-num=\"01004 01\">family</st>,<n id=\"2\" /> but <st data-num=\"03808\" class=\"\">remove</st> the <st data-num=\"04046\" class=\"\">plague</st> from your <st data-num=\"05971\" class=\"\">people</st>!\u201d<n id=\"3\" /> </p>",
    "verse": "17"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "1 Chronicles",
    "chapter": "21",
    "text": "<p class=\"bodytext\">So the <st data-num=\"04397\" class=\"\">angel</st> of the <span class=\"smcaps\"><st data-num=\"03068\" class=\"\">Lord</st></span> <st data-num=\"0559 0413\">told</st> <st data-num=\"01410\" class=\"\">Gad</st> to <st data-num=\"0559\" class=\"\">instruct</st> <st data-num=\"01732\" class=\"\">David</st> <st data-num=\"03588\" class=\"\">to</st> <st data-num=\"05927 01732\">go up</st> and <st data-num=\"06965\" class=\"\">build</st><n id=\"1\" /> an <st data-num=\"04196\" class=\"\">altar</st> for the <span class=\"smcaps\"><st data-num=\"03068\" class=\"\">Lord</st></span> on the <st data-num=\"01637\" class=\"\">threshing floor</st> of <st data-num=\"0771\" class=\"\">Ornan</st> the <st data-num=\"02983\" class=\"\">Jebusite</st>. ",
    "verse": "18"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "1 Chronicles",
    "chapter": "21",
    "text": "So <st data-num=\"01732\" class=\"\">David</st> <st data-num=\"05927\" class=\"\">went up</st> <st data-num=\"01697 0834\">as</st> <st data-num=\"01410\" class=\"\">Gad</st> <st data-num=\"01696\" class=\"\">instructed</st> him to do in the <st data-num=\"08034\" class=\"\">name</st> of the <span class=\"smcaps\"><st data-num=\"03068\" class=\"\">Lord</st></span>.<n id=\"1\" /> ",
    "verse": "19"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "1 Chronicles",
    "chapter": "21",
    "text": "While <st data-num=\"0771\" class=\"\">Ornan</st> was <st data-num=\"01758\" class=\"\">threshing</st> <st data-num=\"02406\" class=\"\">wheat</st>, <st data-num=\"0771\" class=\"\">he</st> <st data-num=\"07725\" class=\"\">turned</st> and <st data-num=\"07200\" class=\"\">saw</st> the <st data-num=\"04397\" class=\"\">messenger</st>, and <st data-num=\"05973\" class=\"\">he</st> and his <st data-num=\"0702\" class=\"\">four</st> <st data-num=\"01121\" class=\"\">sons</st> <st data-num=\"02244\" class=\"\">hid</st> themselves.",
    "verse": "20"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "1 Chronicles",
    "chapter": "21",
    "text": "When <st data-num=\"01732\" class=\"\">David</st> <st data-num=\"0935\" class=\"\">came</st> <st data-num=\"05704\" class=\"\">to</st> <st data-num=\"0771\" class=\"\">Ornan</st>, <st data-num=\"0771\" class=\"\">Ornan</st> <st data-num=\"05027\" class=\"\">looked</st> and <st data-num=\"07200\" class=\"\">saw</st> <st data-num=\"01732\" class=\"\">David</st>; he <st data-num=\"03318\" class=\"\">came out</st> <st data-num=\"04480\" class=\"\">from</st> the <st data-num=\"01637\" class=\"\">threshing floor</st> and <st data-num=\"07812\" class=\"\">bowed</st> to <st data-num=\"01732\" class=\"\">David</st> with his <st data-num=\"0639\" class=\"\">face</st><n id=\"1\" /> to the <st data-num=\"0776\" class=\"\">ground</st>. ",
    "verse": "21"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "1 Chronicles",
    "chapter": "21",
    "text": "<st data-num=\"01732\" class=\"\">David</st> <st data-num=\"0559\" class=\"\">said</st> <st data-num=\"0413\" class=\"\">to</st> <st data-num=\"0771\" class=\"\">Ornan</st>, \u201c<st data-num=\"05414\" class=\"\">Sell</st> me the <st data-num=\"04725 01637\">threshing floor</st><n id=\"1\" /> so I can <st data-num=\"01129\" class=\"\">build</st><n id=\"2\" /> on it an <st data-num=\"04196\" class=\"\">altar</st> for the <span class=\"smcaps\"><st data-num=\"03068\" class=\"\">Lord</st></span>\u2014I\u2019ll <st data-num=\"05414\" class=\"\">pay</st> <st data-num=\"04392\" class=\"\">top</st> <st data-num=\"03701\" class=\"\">price</st><n id=\"3\" />\u2014so that the <st data-num=\"04046\" class=\"\">plague</st> may be <st data-num=\"06113\" class=\"\">removed</st><n id=\"4\" /> <st data-num=\"05921\" class=\"\">from</st> the <st data-num=\"05971\" class=\"\">people</st>.\u201d ",
    "verse": "22"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "1 Chronicles",
    "chapter": "21",
    "text": "<st data-num=\"0771\" class=\"\">Ornan</st> <st data-num=\"0559 0413\">told</st> <st data-num=\"01732\" class=\"\">David</st>, \u201cYou can <st data-num=\"03947\" class=\"\">have</st> it!<n id=\"1\" /> My <st data-num=\"0113\" class=\"\">master</st>, the <st data-num=\"04428\" class=\"\">king</st>, may <st data-num=\"06213\" class=\"\">do</st> what he <st data-num=\"02896 05869\">wants</st>.<n id=\"2\" /> <st data-num=\"07200\" class=\"\">Look</st>, I am <st data-num=\"05414\" class=\"\">giving</st> you the <st data-num=\"01241\" class=\"\">oxen</st> for <st data-num=\"05930\" class=\"\">burnt sacrifices</st>, the <st data-num=\"04173\" class=\"\">threshing sledges</st> for <st data-num=\"06086\" class=\"\">wood</st>, and the <st data-num=\"02406\" class=\"\">wheat</st> for an <st data-num=\"04503\" class=\"\">offering</st>. I <st data-num=\"05414\" class=\"\">give</st> it <st data-num=\"03605\" class=\"\">all</st> to you.\u201d",
    "verse": "23"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "1 Chronicles",
    "chapter": "21",
    "text": "<st data-num=\"04428\" class=\"\">King</st> <st data-num=\"01732\" class=\"\">David</st> <st data-num=\"0559\" class=\"\">replied</st> to <st data-num=\"0771\" class=\"\">Ornan</st>, \u201c<st data-num=\"03808\" class=\"\">No</st>, I <st data-num=\"03588 07069\">insist on</st> <st data-num=\"07069\" class=\"\">buying</st> it for <st data-num=\"04392\" class=\"\">top</st> <st data-num=\"03701\" class=\"\">price</st>.<n id=\"1\" /> I will <st data-num=\"03588 03808\">not</st> <st data-num=\"05375\" class=\"\">offer</st> to the <span class=\"smcaps\"><st data-num=\"03068\" class=\"\">Lord</st></span> <st data-num=\"0834\">what</st> belongs to you or <st data-num=\"05927\" class=\"\">offer</st> a <st data-num=\"05930\" class=\"\">burnt sacrifice</st><n id=\"2\" /> that <st data-num=\"02600\" class=\"\">cost</st> me <st data-num=\"02600\" class=\"\">nothing</st>.<n id=\"3\" />",
    "verse": "24"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "1 Chronicles",
    "chapter": "21",
    "text": "So <st data-num=\"01732\" class=\"\">David</st> <st data-num=\"05414\" class=\"\">bought</st> the <st data-num=\"04725\" class=\"\">place</st> from <st data-num=\"0771\" class=\"\">Ornan</st> <st data-num=\"04948\" class=\"\">for</st> <st data-num=\"08337 03967\">600</st> <st data-num=\"08255\" class=\"\">pieces</st> of <st data-num=\"02091\" class=\"\">gold</st>.<n id=\"1\" /> ",
    "verse": "25"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "1 Chronicles",
    "chapter": "21",
    "text": "<st data-num=\"01732\" class=\"\">David</st> <st data-num=\"01129\" class=\"\">built</st> <st data-num=\"08033\" class=\"\">there</st> an <st data-num=\"04196\" class=\"\">altar</st> to the <span class=\"smcaps\"><st data-num=\"03068\" class=\"\">Lord</st></span> and <st data-num=\"05927\" class=\"\">offered</st> <st data-num=\"05930\" class=\"\">burnt sacrifices</st> and <st data-num=\"08002\" class=\"\">peace offerings</st>.<n id=\"1\" /> He <st data-num=\"07121\" class=\"\">called out</st> <st data-num=\"0413\" class=\"\">to</st> the <span class=\"smcaps\"><st data-num=\"03068\" class=\"\">Lord</st></span>, and the <span class=\"smcaps\">Lord</span><n id=\"2\" /> <st data-num=\"06030\" class=\"\">responded</st> by sending <st data-num=\"0784\" class=\"\">fire</st> <st data-num=\"04480\" class=\"\">from</st> the <st data-num=\"08064\" class=\"\">sky</st> and consuming the <st data-num=\"05930\" class=\"\">burnt sacrifice</st> <st data-num=\"05921\" class=\"\">on</st> the <st data-num=\"04196\" class=\"\">altar</st>. ",
    "verse": "26"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "1 Chronicles",
    "chapter": "21",
    "text": "The <span class=\"smcaps\"><st data-num=\"03068\" class=\"\">Lord</st></span> <st data-num=\"0559\" class=\"\">ordered</st> the <st data-num=\"04397\" class=\"\">messenger</st><n id=\"1\" /> to <st data-num=\"07725\" class=\"\">put</st> his <st data-num=\"02719\" class=\"\">sword</st> <st data-num=\"07725\" class=\"\">back</st> <st data-num=\"0413\" class=\"\">into</st> its <st data-num=\"05084\" class=\"\">sheath</st>. </p>",
    "verse": "27"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "1 Chronicles",
    "chapter": "21",
    "text": "<p class=\"bodytext\">At <st data-num=\"01931\" class=\"\">that</st> <st data-num=\"06256\" class=\"\">time</st>, when <st data-num=\"01732\" class=\"\">David</st> <st data-num=\"07200\" class=\"\">saw</st> <st data-num=\"03588\" class=\"\">that</st> the <span class=\"smcaps\"><st data-num=\"03068\" class=\"\">Lord</st></span> <st data-num=\"06030\" class=\"\">responded</st> to him at the <st data-num=\"01637\" class=\"\">threshing floor</st> of <st data-num=\"0771\" class=\"\">Ornan</st> the <st data-num=\"02983\" class=\"\">Jebusite</st>, he <st data-num=\"02076\" class=\"\">sacrificed</st> <st data-num=\"08033\" class=\"\">there</st>. ",
    "verse": "28"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "1 Chronicles",
    "chapter": "21",
    "text": "Now the <span class=\"smcaps\"><st data-num=\"03068\" class=\"\">Lord</st></span>\u2019s <st data-num=\"04908\" class=\"\">tabernacle</st> (<st data-num=\"0834\" class=\"\">which</st> <st data-num=\"04872\" class=\"\">Moses</st> had <st data-num=\"06213\" class=\"\">made</st> in the <st data-num=\"04057\" class=\"\">wilderness</st>) and the <st data-num=\"04196\" class=\"\">altar</st> for <st data-num=\"05930\" class=\"\">burnt sacrifices</st> were at <st data-num=\"01931\" class=\"\">that</st> <st data-num=\"06256\" class=\"\">time</st> at the <st data-num=\"01116\" class=\"\">worship center</st><n id=\"1\" /> in <st data-num=\"01391\" class=\"\">Gibeon</st>. ",
    "verse": "29"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "1 Chronicles",
    "chapter": "21",
    "text": "But <st data-num=\"01732\" class=\"\">David</st> <st data-num=\"03201\" class=\"\">could</st> <st data-num=\"03808\" class=\"\">not</st> <st data-num=\"01980\" class=\"\">go</st> <st data-num=\"06440\" class=\"\">before</st> it to <st data-num=\"01875\" class=\"\">seek</st> <st data-num=\"0430\" class=\"\">God\u2019s</st> will, <st data-num=\"03588\" class=\"\">for</st> he was <st data-num=\"01204\" class=\"\">afraid</st> <st data-num=\"06440\" class=\"\">of</st> the <st data-num=\"02719\" class=\"\">sword</st> of the <st data-num=\"04397\" class=\"\">angel</st> of the <span class=\"smcaps\"><st data-num=\"03068\" class=\"\">Lord</st></span>. ",
    "verse": "30"
  }
]